  <h2>Using Frost Probability for Seed Starting</h2>

  <p>
    Your last frost date anchors your indoor start schedule.
  </p>

  <ol>
    <li>Find your average last frost date.</li>
    <li>Count backward the recommended number of weeks.</li>
    <li>Adjust based on soil temperature and nighttime lows.</li>
  </ol>

